    "overview": "Operative details regarding A number is as much... under the category of Hardware & Software.",
    "question": "A number is as much greater than 36 as is less than 86. Find the number? Let the number be x. The problem states that the number is as much greater than 36 as it is less than 86. This can be expressed as: x-36-86-xx- 36 = 86-xx-36=86-x Simplify the equation: 2x=1222x = 1222x=122 x=61x = 61x=61 Thus, the number is 61.",
