    "reddington_story": "18/5. Speed, precision, timing. Whether you're outrunning a government agency or ensuring a critical delivery arrives exactly when it should, calculating velocity is paramount. A train's speed, a car's acceleration – these aren't just numbers, they're the difference between success and utter failure.",
