    "overview": "Operative details regarding Second constitution of Pakistan was... under the category of Constitutional History.",
    "question": "Second constitution of Pakistan was enforced on? The Second Constitution of Pakistan (the Constitution of 1962) was promulgated on 1st March 1962 but came into force on 8th June 1962. To summarize: • Promulgation date: 1st March 1962 • Enforcement date: 8th June 1962",
